lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;!--&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;伊朗表示，它&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/zd13tcbKe2Pf07X8GpuF68hFuRIwSgs6e_m89jkyvW4ytCSJp6aFKPIeRqy_SoEhfNBc1zJX__hwmEf13ORqdObFuLt1w1mA9W-Rxa0p4_2qaTYOnMYBLfmWxSL04WLVfbUM1Ijt0nS3DLTDpI3MTsmCWhpbrch-7bWfaxasyQvpRlLgyKEG47MIPJFG--oDXL_VFHg28gpDeMD56mIfxLMkqBN-kTd8s5JNrh2IsRjVlngy2OPfAqYLpP5kfJr0AQbo9jo1jRkSiDyQMaGqEAoEoMYpfzQJ3WVUUOnjMlJzvbE8fFcaAvaJgRf-mmQJCk6xkaTYCcrFPfOivpMFIp1bc8f4W4h7yWlEXuRJIz8NsihZOWd2dshktyi0E7_GkoOqqvQikJLr5u8qyJUCGBWtRzXRYesQq1He7Y24vyAj24vTdPbceBcr851rO7akq63YUwEpWCw4rfx8W1x7DAZFE2KnjdNMLZ8NYwMi6KOWKENRdFMC8osJQ7OZ1QM/miPEVX3fiMcd498DzaktHZagap63vKIM/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗拒绝美国和平计划，对结束战争的努力造成打击"&gt;拒绝了美国的停火提议&lt;/a&gt;，并继续&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/j2ZpcFgA29cARiTV1BqQFgZ4FCFDiRLARgR4mGt1HwibLOfBGmp_qhM4e1kbGLZmFi6EEPvh0uZuIxy4wIW_gYxRUf_-EpKGHctH8nLQxAPVtBSUpvct7t0ndgI7CBqg4qdcGZ2onqrJT4mte3ETysJSb7Wq23JPCUdsEgXAUtEYTrBC781JhgpKhOsEoDkn7Vz7aPr6EO50URwYCDoZY4q8-G06yuQSaFsmwJAQYFI8FNesaCCwBN3BZO0sH5ruEJ_7eEKqwpJ-KhDTF80eyHoDQPEp3CRBbllUDV18lyHfrezlpPwvcRj1VqhzmKaGN6rDi3ljtkJjpW0NgoUqdMsqb0kzg6SgcGTf-OhVnDEC_S4Pjf11xqRxjbVJnjdHh2Uu7_70aQL_-IXbyHtsbFAwxj0CC7jYw6JjlZHLWqtdVPjC9us1Eja9aPCi8UD0h5vDKnlolgxpDz6ztHSLRFgUYzR_Xdn_Tys_NsiF3D2AQrMFTRKSEH2KqiFpqQegwfFC/7ZEbxrteDP2Q53-dXwwj37r5x_F_70MX/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗难以追踪的远程导弹造成更大损失"&gt;对以色列和海湾阿拉伯国家进行攻击&lt;/a&gt;，这对华盛顿结束特朗普政府近一个月前与以色列发动的战争的努力造成了打击。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;据几位知情人士透露，美国的 15 点和平计划规定，伊斯兰共和国&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/oxGCgGUwzhjFzR1gGTHA3TI9tBbUJUrp3VWD1NCvZA8pG3d5NCohHmFA9L-g_SF8bXxuxdTRfWidhjPlPis4kATp3G35jw50AeV6YeEi3PSCv3ZP1183S5xcfIUN3UGt0ujKv0bm6uCXT6QJIiDhr5dM-R3sL1HOi89meREr4wnNlyINvj75uIpz1UUk6CkbfSehPTiI